Description:

Prepare for an extraordinary journey of the senses with Tastebudz Biscotti 33 Strain Autoflower Seeds. This remarkable strain is the harmonious result of blending the renowned Gelato #33 and Sour Kush strains. Let the essence of the Biscotti 33 strain, with its distinctive fruity and uplifting flavours, coupled with the profound relaxation of Sour Kush, transport you to a realm of pure bliss in your own garden. part of the Tastebudz Seeds Auto Mix pack.

 

Indulgence Meets Efficiency:

Experience the captivating embrace of the Biscotti weed strains potent 70% Indica profile. The biscotti 33 strain effects offer an enduring, deep relaxation that unfolds gradually, enveloping both body and mind. With a swift 7-8 week flowering time, these autoflowering seeds yield up to 350-400 g/m² of premium cannabis when cultivated indoors. Outdoor growers can anticipate a bountiful harvest of Biscotti 33 Autoflowering Seeds, ensuring an ample supply for personal enjoyment.

 

Elevate Your Senses With Our Biscotti Strain:

Elevate your senses and embark on a thrilling journey with our Biscotti strain UK, (Biscotti #33 auto) impressive THC content of 25%. Dive into a symphony of terpenes, including Linalool, Alpha Pinene, Limonene, Myrcene, and more. These terpenes contribute to a delightful aroma that perfectly complements the strain’s exceptional effects.

 

Variety Awaits:

Tastebudz Biscotti 33 Autoflowering Seeds are your gateway to a diverse collection of high-quality feminized cannabis seeds. They are part of the Tastebudz Syndicate Autoflowering Mix pack, a treasure trove for collectors seeking exceptional strains.

 

Dive into the World of Biscotti 33:

Please note that Tastebudz Syndicate seeds are exclusively sold as collectible souvenirs in full compliance with U.K. laws. Fortunately, these sensational seeds are available through seedbanks worldwide. Discover your nearest distributor and embark on a journey celebrating the fusion of taste, aroma, and potency. Don’t miss the opportunity to elevate your cannabis cultivation to a realm of unforgettable flavours and sensations. Order your Tastebudz Biscotti 33 Autoflowering Seeds today and join the global community of cannabis connoisseurs savouring the essence of Biscotti #33 auto.
